title: Proxmox VE: VM Backup Status
agents: proxmox_ve
catalog: os/misc
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check is OK when a successful backup has been identified for the given VM which meets the
 configured conditions or if no conditions have been specified.
 The conditions contain maximum ages and optionally the need for absence of a failed backup
 after the last successful one.
 It shows date, age, size and bandwidth of the last successful backup.

inventory:
 One service per system is created.
